  fullBackstory: "Lakap: G\xFCneyin B\xFCy\xFCk \u0130mparatoru / Refah Getiren /
    Zulm\xFCn Habercisi\n\r\nGe\xE7mi\u015F: \xD6nceki hayat\u0131nda \xFClkesine
    ve halk\u0131na refah getirmi\u015F, fakat sava\u015Ft\u0131\u011F\u0131 \xFClkelere
    zulmetmi\u015F ve k\xF6lele\u015Ftirmi\u015F bir imparator.\n\r\n\xD6l\xFCm \u015Fekli:
    Suikast.\n\r\nSon s\xF6z\xFC: \"Sen de mi Br\xFCt\xFCs...\""
  soulCoins: 17
  dialogueLines:
  - text: "Merhaba. Ben Y\xFCce \u0130mparator Argall von Minos. "
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: -8628307796927150301, guid: b8c2e6db68f7e3f4abc0dfccf65710ba, type: 3}
  - text: "Buraya reenkarne olmaya geldim. Umar\u0131m do\u011Fru karar\u0131 verirsin."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: -8628307796927150301, guid: b8c2e6db68f7e3f4abc0dfccf65710ba, type: 3}
